Author: Kat_Von_Diphtheria
Text: You'll be fine, sweetheart.  Yesterday I had strong period cravings and told myself I would go out with my friend only to have something sweet. We ended up having dinner and then going to a cafe to have muffins. It didn't end there, I bought a bag of chips and went home, then I got drunk and binged the whole bag.  It happens. You'll be alright, trust me.
